title: The Night of the Doctor - VOSTFR
description:
This is the prequel to the 50th anniversary episode of Doctor Who : The Night of the Doctor.

I'm uploading this to provide French people a (I hope) decent translation of this minisode.

If you're not French or only want the video, this torrent shall please you as the subtitles are in a .srt seperated file :)

I downloaded the video from the BBC'sone so the quality should be maximum (I didn't do any kind of processing on the video, I only created the subtitles).

Enjoy ! :)
